ZH: 这只猫非常可爱。
EN: This cat is very cute.

ZH: 猫喜欢捉老鼠。
EN: Cats like to catch mice.

ZH: 他家养了一只胖猫。
EN: Their family has a fat cat.

ZH: 猫是家庭的好伴侣。
EN: Cats are good companions for families.

ZH: 他的猫总是在午后睡觉。
EN: His cat always sleeps in the afternoon.

ZH: 这只猫非常狡猾。
EN: This cat is very sly.

ZH: 猫喜欢被搔痒。
EN: Cats like to be scratched.

ZH: 昨天晚上我听到猫的叫声。
EN: I heard the cat meowing last night.

ZH: 猫的天性就是独立。
EN: Cats are naturally independent.

ZH: 她家里有三只猫。
EN: There are three cats in her house.

ZH: 猫的毛发有很多种颜色。
EN: Cats have many different fur colors.

ZH: 有时猫会抓家具。
EN: Sometimes cats scratch furniture.

ZH: 猫可以帮助驱赶老鼠。
EN: Cats can help chase away mice.

ZH: 这只猫很调皮。
EN: This cat is very mischievous.

ZH: 猫可以陪伴人们一生。
EN: Cats can accompany people throughout their lives.

ZH: 我家的猫总是喜欢窝在暖炉旁。
EN: My cat always likes to nest by the fireplace.

ZH: 猫有时会在草丛里玩耍。
EN: Cats sometimes play in the grass.

ZH: 她的猫非常亲近人。
EN: Her cat is very affectionate towards people.

ZH: 猫是我最喜欢的动物之一。
EN: Cats are one of my favorite animals.

ZH: 猫的咪咪声非常动听。
EN: The meowing of cats is very pleasant to listen to.
